title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Feb 21 MO [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Monday, 21 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


Monday's guests: 

Rep. Thaddeus McCotter, Republican congressman from Michigan's 11th district, on his new book, "Seize Freedom; American Truths and Renewal in a Chaotic Age,"

Zach Carter, Huffington Post staff writer and former member of Americans for Financial Reform's steering committee, on why Wall Street "speculators" are to blame for spiking global food prices.
